{"tid":317950,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE]副學士疑難解答","createTime":"2017-07-11T19:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T22:53:47.000Z","uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb8127083c1b97014eb919f58b69bf71cacc7b9","tid":317950,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T19:59:21.000Z","msg":"我當然希望大家直接升u<br />\n不過位就得咁多 總有人要選擇其他升學途徑<br />\n其中副學士最為熱門<br />\n讀得asso 都係為升u<br />\n𣎴論係決定咗讀asso 定係想了解多d asso 既你<br />\n(到底work唔work?難唔難?讀d乜?同HD有乜分別)<br />\n又或者想知過來人心路歷程<br />\n你都可以問<br />\n由其係hkcc 商科<br />\n如果你有大量問題 超多野想問<br />\n可以留個tg 一次過答"},{"pid":"4d0dff62eb3d0908c70b1c51b018741bf47d5fcb","tid":317950,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:01:35.000Z","msg":"asso學生等於垃圾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有堆asshole仔喺呢個po度比純正大學生圍剿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為asshole仔嘅你仲唔快啲過去增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"164a8f73209dd7037cfd78799b9337eaca3c3a75","tid":317950,"uid":122551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:01:57.000Z","msg":"如果攞到個學位但係唔多岩心水係咪最好比5000蚊留位之後再試下報其他Aasso 會好d?"},{"pid":"0252dcbb534f76dd25263f9f624fd08c22630202","tid":317950,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:06:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>asso學生等於垃圾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/293630/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有堆asshole仔喺呢個po度比純正大學生圍剿緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為asshole仔嘅你仲唔快啲過去增援?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n心態問題都好重要<br />\n讀asso既人最常自卑<br />\n我自己都試過 睇住身邊同學升u<br />\n自己就做失敗者<br />\n所以一定要調整心態<br />\n唔好理身邊閒話 做好自己<br />\n把握asso呢次重生機會<br />\ndse已成過去 大家都喺asso呢條起跑線出發"},{"pid":"536b90e368a8093d9eb27dead06afe2a7125cefd","tid":317950,"uid":67606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果攞到個學位但係唔多岩心水係咪最好比5000蚊留位之後再試下報其他Aasso 會好d?</blockquote><br />\n咩offer?<br />\n我建議你先等聽日成績再決定<br />\n唔洗咁急留位<br />\nasso呢d有錢 有十零分就實收<br />\n小心揀科好揀要 <br />\n你冇興趣黎緊兩年會讀到好辛苦"},{"pid":"36f1d3737d9cdeba9cd3a9a58db31d0053e85df9","tid":317950,"uid":67606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88901cfc220dd9a95b966ec2b94234b7ddc86ff1","tid":317950,"uid":122611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T20:25:44.000Z","msg":"讀asso升學率本身已經有30%以上<br />\n比起dse既升學率已經高一截<br />\n如果dse考生冇jupas offer 又想入返八大 asso絕對係比dse更加有利既遊戲黎"},{"pid":"ff86877a9cf3b58ae3ec54ec6100c85173542bcb","tid":317950,"uid":10586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T22:53:47.000Z","msg":"cccu vs hkuspace邊間比較好？<br />\n有冇話邊間啲人偏向讀書多邊間啲人偏向多人玩去蒲之類"}]}